    <j.0:event_legal_comment xml:lang="en">The Commission can accept amendments 2,3,4,5,12,13,14,16,17,18,27 which add precisenes and clarity to this basic act and respect its purpose, however it rejects amendments 6,7,8,9,10,11,19,20, 22 concerning the aspects of the duration of the programme, its evaluation, the extension of the budget and an obligation to inform the EP on the themes decided before launching the open call for proposals. The Commission will incorporate into a revised proposal the elements of those amendments which it fully or partly accepts.</j.0:event_legal_comment>
